<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/24 (Thu) Life is fruity -official Trailer / ‘Big S’ rekindles romance with ancient phone number  (Host: Gal)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=601&amp;p=624#p624"><![CDATA[
Life is fruity -official Trailer/ Call me maybe: ‘Big S’ rekindles romance with ancient phone number <br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session I:<br />Life is fruity- Official Trailer<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SmgV2CfuGes">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SmgV2CfuGes</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Life_Is_Fruity">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Life_Is_Fruity</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br />1.Do you yearn for a rural life?<br />2.Do you have any experience in planting crops or flowers?<br />3.Men want a big toy, such as Shuichi wants a sailboat, Hideko pawned kimonos for him to achieve.  Do you agree with this statement?<br />4.Shuichi refuses many requests for interviews with him and Hideko, saying: &quot;I don't have much time left, I want to enjoy it myself.&quot;  Have you also turned down any activities in order to keep your time?<br /><br /><br />Session II:<br />Call me maybe: ‘Big S’ rekindles romance with ancient phone number <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://taipeitimes.com/News/lang/archives/2022/03/14/2003774714">https://taipeitimes.com/News/lang/archi ... 2003774714</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Have you ever heard of or had a friend or relative you couldn't see because of the pandemic?<br />2.Have you ever heard of or encountered a situation at work where you were unable to travel or foreigners were unable to come to Taiwan because of the pandemic?<br />3.If your answer is yes for Q1 or Q2, how to respond to this kind of situation?<br />4.Someone said: This news has sparked a fire in the hearts of many people. Have you thought of any good news around you or heard this year?...<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Sun Mar 20, 2022 7:37 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
